{"tid":2055441,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭立：西世界 —— 你唔當對方係人，你咪西囉。","createTime":"2020-06-08T03:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T13:11:12.000Z","uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"300fb6eb768908e862a17aad93ea85a812348ee6","tid":2055441,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T03:27:26.000Z","msg":"「西世界（Westworld）」這個美劇，講述近未來有一間公司推出了一種處境遊樂園，但他不是虛擬幻境，也不是電玩，而是用真實的機械人裝成人類，給你體驗古代的西部風情。那些有著完美擬人包裝的機械人，不僅外表，在極度進化的人工智能下，情緒反應皆與人類幾乎一樣，給人猶如時光旅行的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/06/08/chenglap-westworld/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2Fchenglap-westworld%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=c4dd2b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/06/08/chenglap-westworld/</a>"},{"pid":"aef0f256d342554256cf4bc37935604f23fc763a","tid":2055441,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"有幾多人真係會殺NPC？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDarksoul 除咗會主動攻擊我嗰啲 我都唔係好敢殺<br />\nUndertale 淨係玩咗一次正常結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0c960074df45a6195f738d4703fdc828601c77","tid":2055441,"uid":286155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aef0f256d342554256cf4bc37935604f23fc763a","tid":2055441,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"有幾多人真係會殺NPC？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDarksoul 除咗會主動攻擊我嗰啲 我都唔係好敢殺<br />\nUndertale 淨係玩咗一次正常結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"以前會<br />\n直到我殺左一隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84c3c864eb63aeeeed9508dc6d2f71ca80a0ca3","tid":2055441,"uid":269061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04